{"tid":2335942,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警方凍結星火等社運戶口逾九千萬元　惟一年後仍未向法庭申令","createTime":"2020-12-22T08:52:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-22T10:39:08.000Z","uid":14918,"like":5,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"befcd1014a958046bc0d806a2f966e0145428fe5","tid":2335942,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T08:52:17.000Z","msg":"警方凍結星火等社運戶口逾九千萬元　惟一年後仍未向法庭申令<br />\n<br />\n【有線新聞】警方以涉嫌洗黑錢，凍結多個社運眾籌戶口超過9,000萬。其中星火同盟，據了解事隔一年警方仍未向法庭申請凍結令，只是指令銀行不准提款，但警方指引列明有關機制一般不應超過半年。<br />\n<br />\n接連有多宗涉及眾籌的洗黑錢案，被警方凍結資金，最大一筆要數到一年前的星火同盟，凍結了約7,000萬。毒品調查科署理高級警陳偉基：「我們會準備申請凍結令。」不過事隔一年，據了解警方尚未正式向法庭申請凍結令。至於被捕的四人，其中三人獲保釋候查，明年再報到，其餘一人拒絕保釋，警方保留檢控權利。（全文）<br />\n<br />\n#20201222新聞"},{"pid":"c21e1db14eaf261b8a749c4da496c30da0fcf370","tid":2335942,"uid":171074,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T08:55:57.000Z","msg":"出把口就封得？"},{"pid":"53edd2d3fbd7c77006b0980d22b1e83e908737b9","tid":2335942,"uid":14918,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"c21e1db14eaf261b8a749c4da496c30da0fcf370","tid":2335942,"uid":171074,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T08:55:57.000Z","msg":"出把口就封得？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T09:03:55.000Z","msg":"而家擺明係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9225ef67fc2b0a94c5cb658833ec1d467c7e474c","tid":2335942,"uid":171074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T09:19:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"654fb86ad5e027bd01a487dfdabf185aa08e6c00","tid":2335942,"uid":310867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T09:29:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5389cee41a77fb581dd302ba9ddeccea53f63bbc","tid":2335942,"uid":263648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"befcd1014a958046bc0d806a2f966e0145428fe5